        .. rubric:: Basic rules

        .. math::

           x + y &=& y + x

           (x+y)+z&=& x+(y+z)

           x+x&=&x

           (x+y)\cdot z &=& (x\cdot z) + (y\cdot z)

           (x \cdot y)\cdot z &=& x \cdot (y \cdot z)

        .. rubric:: Deadlock

        .. math::

           \delta + x &=& x

           \delta \cdot x &=& \delta

        All formulas from `wikipedia <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algebra_of_communicating_processes>`__

